{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.1","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:1","prev_osis_id":"Col.003.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Ma\u00eetres, accordez \u00e0 vos serviteurs ce qui est juste et \u00e9quitable, sachant que vous aussi vous avez un ma\u00eetre dans le ciel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.2","name":"Colossiens 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.3.25","name":"Colossiens 3:25","id":"fra-LSG:Col.3.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.2","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:2","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exhortation \u00e0 la pri\u00e8re et \u00e0 la sagesse<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 2-6: cf. \u00c9p 8:18-20; 5:14-17; 4:27.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>\n    Pers\u00e9v\u00e9rez dans la pri\u00e8re, veillez-y avec actions de gr\u00e2ces.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.3","name":"Colossiens 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.1","name":"Colossiens 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.3","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:3","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Priez en m\u00eame temps pour nous, afin que Dieu nous ouvre une porte pour la parole, en sorte que je puisse annoncer le myst\u00e8re de Christ, pour lequel je suis dans les cha\u00eenes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.4","name":"Colossiens 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.2","name":"Colossiens 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.4","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:4","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>et le faire conna\u00eetre comme je dois en parler.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.5","name":"Colossiens 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.3","name":"Colossiens 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.5","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:5","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Conduisez-vous avec sagesse envers ceux du dehors, et rachetez le temps.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.6","name":"Colossiens 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.4","name":"Colossiens 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.6","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:6","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Que votre parole soit toujours accompagn\u00e9e de gr\u00e2ce, assaisonn\u00e9e de sel, afin que vous sachiez comment il faut r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 chacun.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.7","name":"Colossiens 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.5","name":"Colossiens 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.7","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:7","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Envoi de Tychique et d\u2019On\u00e9sime. Salutations<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-18: cf. \u00c9p 6:21, 22. (Col 1:7, 8. Ph 2:10-25.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>\n    Tychique, le bien-aim\u00e9 fr\u00e8re et le fid\u00e8le ministre, mon compagnon de service dans le Seigneur, vous communiquera tout ce qui me concerne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.8","name":"Colossiens 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.6","name":"Colossiens 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.8","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:8","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Je l\u2019envoie expr\u00e8s vers vous, pour que vous connaissiez notre situation, et pour qu\u2019il console vos c\u0153urs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.9","name":"Colossiens 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.7","name":"Colossiens 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.9","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:9","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Je l\u2019envoie avec On\u00e9sime, le fid\u00e8le et bien-aim\u00e9 fr\u00e8re, qui est des v\u00f4tres. Ils vous informeront de tout ce qui se passe ici.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.10","name":"Colossiens 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.8","name":"Colossiens 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.10","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:10","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Aristarque, mon compagnon de captivit\u00e9, vous salue, ainsi que Marc, le cousin de Barnabas, au sujet duquel vous avez re\u00e7u des ordres (s\u2019il va chez vous, accueillez-le);<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.11","name":"Colossiens 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.9","name":"Colossiens 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.11","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:11","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>J\u00e9sus, appel\u00e9 Justus, vous salue aussi. Ils sont du nombre des circoncis, et les seuls qui aient travaill\u00e9 avec moi pour le royaume de Dieu, et qui aient \u00e9t\u00e9 pour moi une consolation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.12","name":"Colossiens 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.10","name":"Colossiens 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.12","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:12","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>\u00c9paphras, qui est des v\u00f4tres, vous salue: serviteur de J\u00e9sus-Christ, il ne cesse de combattre pour vous dans ses pri\u00e8res, afin que, parfaits et pleinement persuad\u00e9s, vous persistiez dans une enti\u00e8re soumission \u00e0 la volont\u00e9 de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.13","name":"Colossiens 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.11","name":"Colossiens 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.13","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:13","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Car je lui rends le t\u00e9moignage qu\u2019il a une grande sollicitude pour vous, pour ceux de Laodic\u00e9e, et pour ceux d\u2019Hi\u00e9rapolis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.14","name":"Colossiens 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.12","name":"Colossiens 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.14","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:14","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Luc, le m\u00e9decin bien-aim\u00e9, vous salue, ainsi que D\u00e9mas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.15","name":"Colossiens 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.13","name":"Colossiens 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.15","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:15","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Saluez les fr\u00e8res qui sont \u00e0 Laodic\u00e9e, et Nymphas, et l\u2019\u00c9glise qui est dans sa maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.16","name":"Colossiens 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.14","name":"Colossiens 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.16","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:16","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Lorsque cette lettre aura \u00e9t\u00e9 lue chez vous, faites en sorte qu\u2019elle soit aussi lue dans l\u2019\u00c9glise des Laodic\u00e9ens, et que vous lisiez \u00e0 votre tour celle qui vous arrivera de Laodic\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.17","name":"Colossiens 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.15","name":"Colossiens 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.17","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:17","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Col.004.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Et dites \u00e0 Archippe: Prends garde au minist\u00e8re que tu as re\u00e7u dans le Seigneur, afin de le bien remplir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.18","name":"Colossiens 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.16","name":"Colossiens 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Col.4.18","label":"","reference":"Colossiens 4:18","prev_osis_id":"Col.004.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Col.4.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Je vous salue, moi Paul, de ma propre main. Souvenez-vous de mes liens. Que la gr\u00e2ce soit avec vous!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Col.4","name":"Colossiens 4","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.1.1","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Col.4.17","name":"Colossiens 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Col.4.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbb59adc8.62823529');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbb59adc8.62823529\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbb59adc8.62823529","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbb59adc8.62823529'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbb59adc8.62823529\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}